# ROI tool

### Form Field Mapping

| Question | Input Type | Values (Dropdown Examples) | Purpose |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| What process do you want to automate? | Dropdown | Invoicing / Data Entry / HR Onboarding / Reporting / Custom Process | To match to services later |
| Frequency of process per month? | Dropdown (range) | 1-10 / 11-50 / 51-100 / 100+ | Calculates total workload |
| Duration per execution? | Dropdown (minutes) | <5 / 5-15 / 15-30 / 30-60 / 60+ | Workload + cost calc |
| Monthly salary of executor? | Dropdown (range) | <1k / 1-2k / 2-3k / 3-5k / 5k+ | Manual cost basis |
| Systems involved? | Dropdown (number) | 1 / 2 / 3-5 / 5+ | Complexity factor for time & cost estimation |

### Process Flow

User lands on page → User fills dropdown form → Form submission → Backend API → Calculate current manual cost → Estimate automation cost (20-30% of created value) → Select matching service (Rule-based) → Generate chart data → Frontend: Loading message ("Calculating your savings…") → Frontend: Show results page (summary + chart + CTA)

### Technical flowchart

User lands on ROI Calculator page → Step 1: User fills out form (Dropdowns only for clean data) → Step 2: User submits form → Frontend sends POST request to Backend API → Backend receives data (Store raw input in database) → Backend Processing (Calculate manual process cost, Estimate automation cost, Map process type to service offer, Estimate implementation time, Prepare chart data) → Backend sends response to frontend (Summary text, Chart data) → Frontend "Loading your results..." screen → Frontend displays Results Page (Summary of calculation, Chart visualization, Optional CTA) → Optional: User clicks CTA → Backend logs CTA click for analytics

### Simple calculation logic

Manual Cost Calculation: Executions per month × Duration (minutes) × (Monthly salary / Monthly working minutes)

Automation Cost Estimate: Manual cost × 20-30%

Implementation Time Estimate: Mapping table: 1 System: 1-2 weeks, 2-3 Systems: 2-4 weeks, 5+ Systems: 4-6 weeks

Solution Mapping: Invoicing → "RPA + Document AI", Data Entry → "RPA + Workflow Automation", HR Onboarding → "Workflow Automation + Integration", Reporting → "BI Automation + Data Integration"

### Screen 1: Form Page

- ROI Calculator title
- Dropdown questions: Process type, Process frequency, Time spent per process, Executor’s salary, Number of systems
- Submit Button: "Calculate Savings"

### Screen 2: Loading Page

- Message: "Your savings are being calculated..."
- Animated spinner or progress bar

### Screen 3: Results Page

- Summary of results: Current process cost, Estimated automation cost, Estimated savings, Estimated implementation time, Solution recommendation
- Chart.js visualization
- CTA Button: "Book Free Consultation"

### Backend Structure

API Endpoint: POST /api/calculate-roi
Input Schema (JSON):
{
  "processType": "Data Entry",
  "frequencyPerMonth": "51-100",
  "timePerProcess": "15-30",
  "monthlySalary": "2-3k",
  "systemsInvolved": "3-5"
}

Output Schema (JSON):
{
  "currentCost": 1200,
  "automationCost": 350,
  "savings": 850,
  "implementationTime": "2-4 weeks",
  "recommendedSolution": "Workflow Automation + Integration",
  "chartData": {
    "labels": ["Current Cost", "Automation Cost", "Savings"],
    "values": [1200, 350, 850]
  }
}

Database Table: submissions
| ID | Timestamp | Process Type | Frequency | Time per Process | Salary Range | Systems Involved | Current Cost | Automation Cost | Solution Recommendation | CTA Clicked (yes/no) |

Backend Calculation Logic:

function calculateROI(input) {
  const salaryMap = {
    "<1k": 750,
    "1-2k": 1500,
    "2-3k": 2500,
    "3-5k": 4000,
    "5k+": 6000
  };
  const timePerProcessMap = {
    "<5": 3,
    "5-15": 10,
    "15-30": 22,
    "30-60": 45,
    "60+": 75
  };
  const frequencyMap = {
    "1-10": 5,
    "11-50": 30,
    "51-100": 75,
    "100+": 150
  };
  const implementationTimeMap = {
    "1": "1-2 weeks",
    "2": "2-4 weeks",
    "3-5": "3-5 weeks",
    "5+": "4-6 weeks"
  };
  const solutionsMap = {
    "Invoicing": "RPA + Document AI",
    "Data Entry": "RPA + Workflow Automation",
    "HR Onboarding": "Workflow Automation + Integration",
    "Reporting": "BI Automation + Data Integration",
    "Other": "Custom Automation Solution"
  };
  const monthlySalary = salaryMap[input.monthlySalary];
  const timePerProcess = timePerProcessMap[input.timePerProcess];
  const frequency = frequencyMap[input.frequencyPerMonth];
  const costPerMinute = monthlySalary / (160 * 60);
  const currentCost = costPerMinute * timePerProcess * frequency;
  const automationCost = currentCost * 0.25;
  const savings = currentCost - automationCost;
  const implementationTime = implementationTimeMap[input.systemsInvolved];
  const recommendedSolution = solutionsMap[input.processType];
  return {
    currentCost: Math.round(currentCost),
    automationCost: Math.round(automationCost),
    savings: Math.round(savings),
    implementationTime,
    recommendedSolution,
    chartData: {
      labels: ["Current Cost", "Automation Cost", "Savings"],
      values: [Math.round(currentCost), Math.round(automationCost), Math.round(savings)]
    }
  };
}
